From mutt CVS:
Fix browse_get_namespace() which could overflow ns[LONG_STRING].
(Possible remote vulnerability)

--- imap/browse.c.orig	Tue Feb 26 11:38:56 2002
+++ imap/browse.c	Tue Jun 20 15:44:27 2006
